snippet.title: KABY ARENA Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Kaby Arena is a Free to Play turn based RPG game, featuring countless unique NFT heroes and equipment. 

⭐️Available to everybody, without upfront investment.
⭐️Unique interaction with the cryptocurrency market.
⭐️Play to earn free tokens.
⭐️Powered by Polygon protocol.
⭐️IDO coming soon on DAO Maker and Red Kite.

Website: https://kabyarena.com/
Annoucements: https://t.me/KabyArenaAnnoucement
Telegram: https://t.me/KabyArena
